    • Class il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.dataset1.domains.container_management.hit.ContainerManagementStateVisualizer extends il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.core.dataset.visualization.StateVisualizer implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      7774549385090549119L

      • Serialized Fields

        • containerPositionToId

          com.ofergivoli.ojavalib.data_structures.map.SafeMap<K,V> containerPositionToId
          A map from the an index in ContainerManagementSystem.containers of the state sent to ContainerManagementStateVisualizer.setContainerPositionsByState(State), and the the id of the ShippingContainer. When not null, the position of the containers in the visualization is determined by this map. Use this map to make containers keep their exact location (pixel-wise) in the visualization even when lower-index containers are removed.
